item.title: The group grows
item.description: Olga Tsoy will join as a Post-Doc. Amit Fenn and Gihanna Galindez join as PhD Students. Tim Faro, Judith Bernett, Andreas Stelzer, Christoph Kloppert and Fanny Rößler decided to do their Bachelor’s thesis with us.
